Netwrix Support Ticket #412076 - Duplicated logs for the same event

TextBody:
Hello Deepti,

I asked the engineers about this issue and I got the following explanations:
For the first screenshot, the threat reported is probably the same (even though we can't see it entirely, since it is obfuscated), but it is reported from different files (sharedstrings.xml and sheet12.xml).
We are aware of this limitation and we will try to handle it in the future.

As for the second screenshot, we can see that the reported file is exactly the same.
In this case, we suspect that the reported threat is not the same. We canâ€™t say this for sure (since the threat is obfuscated), but this could be checked on your side, if you have access to the file which was sent. You will have to look in the file and check if the 2 bank accounts are the same or different.
Let us know if the data sets which were reported are the same or if they are different. If they are the same, there might be an issue on our side.

Best regards,
Emil
